    "The datasets used in those experiments were selected in a manner that matches realistic business environments.",
    "They include various types of network traffic and intrusions that may exist in a mission field using UAVs.",
    "The datasets give a range of intrusions such as DoS, unauthorized access, probing, etc.",
    "This diversity ensures that intrusion detection models are exposed to a wide range of challenges, increasing their immunity to new challenges.",
    "These datasets, therefore, act as the gold standard against which the performance of intrusion detection models can be measured."
